songs.title: Calculator
songs.lyrics:
*Lyrics From Snippet*

[Intro: Isaiah Rashad]
Ooh, yeah

[Chorus: Isaiah Rashad]
Calculator, you bring me up to you (Ooh-ooh)
Calculator, you bring me up to you (Ooh-ooh)
I ain't got nothing to wait
Ain't got nothing to feel
I'm at the Kingdom
I ain't got nothing to wait
Ain't got nothing to feel
I'm at the Kingdom, at the kingdom

[Verse 1: Isaiah Rashad]
But still, still cover my face
Still breaking my mind (Still), still breaking my shine (Still)
Still smoking on time (Still), still stretching my breaks
Still stretching my thighs (Still), still banging on fakes
